d94c-9e8f-4d22-8f25-67afacbd31c2","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#inbox-ops","cachedResultName":"#inbox-ops"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3618,1420],"id":"8e8a5779-60e6-4d73-aae9-75097144bb16","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### New Email Form Submission\n\nServes an n8n-hosted form (From, Subject, Receivedat). Each submission becomes one execution.\n\nNext: Stamp & Shape Email","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"654a3f1b-5cc5-c1aa-7e13-e13102ca5082","name":"Note: New Email Form Submission"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp & Shape Email\n\nShapes the item: writes `messageId`, `receivedAt`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Payload Valid?","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"db905fc8-0646-3843-4b79-06828cd89b76","name":"Note: Stamp & Shape Email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Payload Valid?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.messageId }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Prepare Approval Packet · ②→ Record Rejected Input","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"5392f8fb-5706-2dc4-498b-0f8e2917a1ae","name":"Note: Payload Valid?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Rejected Input\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,1030],"id":"af0eade8-db5a-48b9-89c8-5cdb2a2b9f73","name":"Note: Record Rejected Input"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Prepare Approval Packet\n\nShapes the item: writes `requestId`, `summary`, `requestedBy`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Request Approval via Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,520],"id":"7458ce0f-fcd0-6f66-166f-00e8f115e74f","name":"Note: Prepare Approval Packet"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Request Approval via Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Hold for Decision · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,520],"id":"1c0b3b6a-ff17-4852-14fb-53adc2af5b6b","name":"Note: Request Approval via Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold for Decision\n\nPauses the execution until the resume webhook is called — this is the approval/HITL gate.\n\nNext: Approved?","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,520],"id":"7f82556d-3c10-0d71-95b7-efb9435b4aec","name":"Note: Hold for Decision"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Approved?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.body?.decision || $json.decision }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Apply Approved Change (Airtable) · ②→ Record Decline + Notify Requester","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"f586a17f-e4dc-bccd-625a-304b26e402b6","name":"Note: Approved?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Apply Approved Change (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1938,280],"id":"151a662d-da73-742c-9af8-17be682dc448","name":"Note: Apply Approved Change (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Record Decline + Notify Requester\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Join Decision Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,880],"id":"0381159a-24bc-792b-6d2d-b3fbb94d4acc","name":"Note: Record Decline + Notify Requester"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Join Decision Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"d8af23f4-c956-795b-893d-0606053dc672","name":"Note: Join Decision Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"ab606bc3-74e6-e845-2f47-1b754b218781","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,1540],"id":"c96e5ea8-ec8c-3a47-492f-f0b11b2d2fb1","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,1540],"id":"2641559c-3f78-1d42-94c4-b5d446ab7e37","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Save form submissions with Airtable and Twilio without manual work\n\n**Pattern:** Form Intake · **Level:** Core · **Trigger:** Form\n\n## What it does\nSave form submissions with Airtable and Twilio without manual work. It starts from a hosted form submission.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual inbox triage is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nNew Email Form Submission → Stamp & Shape Email → Payload Valid? → Prepare Approval Packet → Request Approval via Slack → Hold for Decision → Approved? → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to form intake without manual effort\n- Anyone automating inbox triage in marketing\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"de74133b-726b-a08b-3aa8-666a26839480","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"dc85bd03-4f66-daff-db41-36519e544586","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"4b48f490-0608-ce48-7132-8a96d62e6d73","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🙋 Human in the loop\n\nThe workflow pauses at the Wait node until a human posts a decision to the resume URL (included in the approval message). Approve → the action executes; anything else → recorded as declined. No timeout is set by default — add one under the Wait node's options if approvals go stale.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"e8cd2fc0-b5ac-b461-2fe4-81d82cc0cef5","name":"🙋 Human in the loop"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your inbox triage process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"c363ccc4-fd2e-8cdc-adc0-9f51d214d88d","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"New Email Form Submission":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp & Shape Email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp & Shape Email":{"main":[[{"node":"Payload Valid?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Payload Valid?":{"main":[[{"node":"Prepare Approval Packet","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Rejected Input","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Prepare Approval Packet":{"main":[[{"node":"Request Approval via Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Request Approval via Slack":{"main":[[{"node":"Hold for Decision","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Hold for Decision":{"main":[[{"node":"Approved?","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Approved?":{"main":[[{"node":"Apply Approved Change (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Record Decline + Notify Requester","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Apply Approved Change (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Decision Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Record Decline + Notify Requester":{"main":[[{"node":"Join Decision Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Join Decision Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"9e33f2d8-74c1-4a47-af5e-f4b2cfe4e0d0","id":"FDX02458"}